OL,3,CFormer NFU President: 'My farming
OL,4,Cmanifesto'
OL,6,FWatch Caron Bell's report
OL,8,FThe rolling fields of Wiltshire feel a
OL,9,Flong way from Westminster, but they
OL,10,Fare home to one of farming's most
OL,11,Finfluential figures.
OL,13,FAs President of the National Farmers'
OL,14,FUnion, Minette Batters has spent six
OL,15,Fyears representing the UK's #14
OL,16,Fbillion agriculture sector at the
OL,17,Fhighest levels of government.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
