OL,3,CFormer NFU President: 'My farming
OL,4,Cmanifesto'
OL,6,FHaving stepped down this year, she now
OL,7,Ffeels able to speak her mind more
OL,8,Ffreely in the run-up to the election,
OL,9,Fand has mixed feelings about the
OL,10,Fparties' promises.
OL,12,F"All the manifestos are a bit light on
OL,13,Fambition", she told ITV News.
OL,15,FShe says she is "extremely worried"
OL,16,Fthat Labour has only 87 words about
OL,17,Ffood and farming in its manifesto and
OL,18,Fdismisses Reform's plan to tax firms
OL,19,Fwith foreign workers as "bonkers".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
