OL,3,CFormer NFU President: 'My farming
OL,4,Cmanifesto'
OL,6,FAs for the Liberal Democrats, Minette
OL,7,FBatters says she likes their pledge of
OL,8,Fan extra billion pounds for farmers,
OL,9,F"but it's easy to promise that when
OL,10,Fyou know you're not going to be in
OL,11,Fgovernment."
OL,13,FShe's more impressed by the
OL,14,FConservatives, giving them "a big
OL,15,Ftick" for their plan to introduce
OL,16,Flegally-binding targets for UK food
OL,17,Fproduction - the only party to do so.
OL,19,FSo what would Batters put in her
OL,20,Fmanifesto? Money is top of her list.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
