OL,3,CFormer NFU President: 'My farming
OL,4,Cmanifesto'
OL,6,F"The (farming) budget is desperately
OL,7,Fimportant", she said.
OL,9,FCurrently the government pays UK
OL,10,Ffarmers around #2.4 billion a year.
OL,11,FThe Conservatives, Lib Dems, Reform
OL,12,Fand the Greens have promised to
OL,13,Fincrease this; Labour has not.
OL,15,FBatters' second priority, is based
OL,16,Faround food production.
OL,18,F"Setting legally-binding targets for
OL,19,Ffood production. It's bonkers that
OL,20,Fthese other parties don't have a
OL,21,Ftarget", she said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
