OL,3,CFormer NFU President: 'My farming
OL,4,Cmanifesto'
OL,6,FAnd thirdly, food strategy.
OL,8,F"I'd like to see the next government
OL,9,Fcoming in with a meaningful food
OL,10,Fpolicy that is going to really
OL,11,Fenergise the nation to get cooking
OL,12,Ffrom scratch", she said.
OL,14,FMost of all, she says farmers want
OL,15,Fcertainty after a tough decade.
OL,16,FBrexit, Covid, Ukraine, inflation and
OL,17,Fclimate change have all posed huge
OL,18,Fchallenges to the industry.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
