OL,4,Cmanifesto'
OL,6,FBut some of Batters' views are
OL,7,Fcontroversial. She believes the UK can
OL,8,Freach net zero without reducing meat
OL,9,Fand dairy farming, something the
OL,10,Fgovernment's Climate Change Committee
OL,11,Fdisagrees with.
OL,13,FShe dismisses rewilding as "pretty
OL,14,Fdisastrous", and she also wants
OL,15,FBritish farms to be allowed to hire
OL,16,Fmore foreign workers.
OL,18,FSo who is Minette Batters voting for
OL,19,Fin her Salisbury constituency?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
